(at the break time at school or at the weekend with friends). Sport is my hobby. It helps me relaxing and energetic. It is also healthy. Spending 30 minutes per day can make my day.


</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-6.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_sports.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Sports</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Do you think children should play team sports? Why?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Do you think children should play team sports? Why?
đôi khi tranh cãi nhưng quan trọng là để ngồi lại, thảo luận để -> solve the problems. từ đó 
1. các kĩ năng.
2.1 gặp nhiều người -> kết bạn mới.
2. healthy -> keep fit/30 mỗi ngày làm nên 1 ngày.
Yes, absolutely.
Sometimes, children can face conflicts but it is important for them to sit down and discuss to solve the problems. This can teach children and awake many skills like communication skills, friendship, and leadership. Additionally, they can meet many people and make new friends. On of that, sport is very healthy. It helps children to keep fit. 30 minutes per day can make a new day.


</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-9.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_work.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
