I prefer to work in a team. 
-> gặp xung đột. Sometimes, we can face conflicts but we can discuss and sit down together to solve the problems. This awake some skills like friendship, leadership and communication skills
-> kết bạn mới -> Additionally, i can meet many people and make friends with them.
-> on top of that, people can share many ideas and support each other.
This makes the work easier.</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-10.1)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_transport.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">1</div></div>
