                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> How do you usually get to work or school ?
-> I usually go to school by bike because i really care about the environment so i take up a greener lifestyle. Riding a bicycle can reduce pollution, carbon footprint (khí thải cá nhân). This helps me to protect the environment   </p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-10.2)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_transport.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">2</div></div>
                        <div><p class="text-[10px] font-black text-indigo-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Topic: Transport</p><p class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 leading-tight">Is public transportation convenient in your city?</p></div>
                    </div></p><p><strong>Note:</strong> Is public transportation (phương tiện giao thông cộng) convenient in your city?
-> xe bus, tàu điện ngầm.
(không tiện) ->  public transportation is underdeveloped. thiếu phương, phải chờ lâu, ùn tắc giao thông, ô nhiễm, chật chội.
Is public transportation convenient in Viet Nam ?.
I think that public transportation in Viet Nam is underdeveloped. We have to wait for a long time for our turn. There are traffic jams which  is very crowded and polluted.


</p><hr><h3>Part 3: Respond to Questions (ID: P3-10.3)</h3><p><div class="glass-card p-6 flex items-center gap-6 group hover:translate-x-1 transition-all">
                        <div class="relative"><img src="image/topic_transport.png" class="w-20 h-20 rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-lg border-2 border-white" onerror="this.src='data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='400' height='300' viewBox='0 0 400 300'%3E%3Crect width='400' height='300' fill='%236366f1' opacity='0.1'/%3E%3Ctext x='50%25' y='50%25' dominant-baseline='middle' text-anchor='middle' font-family='Outfit' font-weight='800' font-size='24' fill='%236366f1'%3EPart%203 Stimulus%3C/text%3E%3C/svg%3E'"><div class="absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-bold border-2 border-white">3</div></div>
